&lt;p&gt;The &lt;a href="https://commitizen-tools.github.io/commitizen/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"&gt;Commitizen documentation&lt;/a&gt; (MkDocs + Material on GitHub Pages) shows &lt;strong&gt;fenced code blocks that fail to render correctly&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;code&gt;```bash&lt;/code&gt; appears as plain text inside a paragraph, and lines starting with &lt;code&gt;#&lt;/code&gt; in code are even interpreted as &lt;strong&gt;Markdown headings&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;code&gt;&amp;lt;h1&amp;gt;&lt;/code&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Energy Trading</title><link>https://ttw225.github.io/blog/en/projects/energy-trading/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>peter86225+web@gmail.com (Peter Wang)</author><guid>https://ttw225.github.io/blog/en/projects/energy-trading/</guid><description>&lt;div class="coming-soon not-prose rounded-lg border border-neutral-300/70 dark:border-neutral-700/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300"&gt;Content for this section is still in progress. More details will be published here soon.&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Smart Control</title><link>https://ttw225.github.io/blog/en/projects/smart-control/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>peter86225+web@gmail.com (Peter Wang)</author><guid>https://ttw225.github.io/blog/en/projects/smart-control/</guid><description>&lt;div class="coming-soon not-prose rounded-lg border border-neutral-300/70 dark:border-neutral-700/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-neutral-700 dark:text-neutral-300"&gt;Content for this section is still in progress. More details will be published here soon.&lt;/div&gt;</description></item><item><title>Thesis</title><link>https://ttw225.github.io/blog/en/research/thesis/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>peter86225+web@gmail.com (Peter Wang)</author><guid>https://ttw225.github.io/blog/en/research/thesis/</guid><description>&lt;div class="coming-soon not-p